        </p>
        <p class="pkg-desc">some("An amateur radio tool to get you a ballpark estimate of where a given Maidenhead grid square is.")</p>
        <a title="Copy" onclick="document.querySelector('#cmd').select();document.execCommand('copy');"
            alt="Copy on clipboard">
            <i class="fa fa-copy"></i>
        </a>
        <input id="cmd" onclick="this.select();" value="nimble install ballpark" readonly="">
